	"keywords": "Artificial Intelligence, ChatGPT, Plugins",
	"description": "ChatGPT [https://chat.openai.com/] is a highly intelligent auto-completion tool.\nIt takes instructions or questions in natural language and provides good enough\ntext-based outputs. \n\nBut there’s a catch — ChatGPT’s knowledge only goes up until September 2021. So,\nas of writing this blog post (June 2023), the model itself is not aware of any\nevents or data after September 2021.\n\nHere is where ChatGPT plugins [https://openai.com/blog/chatgpt-plugins] come to\nthe rescue. These plugins allow ChatGPT",
